<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.2.7">
<l>vaḷḷi nuṭaṅkiṭai mātar vantalar tūṟṟiṭa</l>
<l>tuḷḷi viḷaiyāṭit tōḻarō ṭutiri yāmē</l>
<l>kaḷḷi yuṇaṅkuveṅ kāṉata riṭaikkaṉ ṟiṉpiṉ</l>
<l>puḷḷiṉ talaivaṉaip pōkkiṉē ṉellēpā vamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To stop him from wandering about frolicking and playing with [his] friends</l>
<l rend="indent">So that ladies with creeper thin waists come spreading gossip</l>
<l>I sent the leader [who rides a] bird after the calves</l>
<l rend="indent">on the hot forest path with dried spurge.</l>
<l>Alas! What a sin!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
